The Grand Prize must be redeemed within the months of July, 2017 or August, 2017 and must be fully booked by Explorers’ Edge and its partner travel agent by June 15, 2017 (based on availability).<br>
Five finalists determined by top votes will receive the Finalist Prize and qualify for the Grand Prize judging.<br>
Throughout the contest, random entrants will be selected to receive ‘Canadian Care Packages.’ These will be chosen at random and are not subject to vote counts.<br>
The prizes are as follows:
      </p>
